== Function ==
This template can be used to link to [[Open Hub]] (formerly Ohloh) project pages.

== Usage ==
To link to a project page, give the registered project name as the first parameter (note: the project name is case-sensitive, and should be all lowercase), and an optional project name as the second parameter. If no name is provided for the second parameter, the template will use the name of the page.

{{Tlx|Openhub|id{{=}}''project ID''|name{{=}}''project name''}}

'''Note''': The "name" parameter is optional. If omitted, the article page title would be used.

===Examples===
;{{Tlx|Openhub|id{{=}}mediawiki|name{{=}}MediaWiki}}
:{{Openhub|id=mediawiki|name=MediaWiki}}
;{{Tlx|Openhub|id{{=}}tidy_for_html5|name{{=}}Tidy for HTML5}}
:{{Openhub|id=tidy_for_html5|name=Tidy for HTML5}}

